Package: rChess
Type: Package
Title: An experimental chess engine written in R with raylibr
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Benjamin Smith
Maintainer: Benjamin Smith <benyamindsmith@gmail.com>
Description: A chess game implementation in R using bindings for raylib. Features a graphical chessboard where users can interact by selecting and moving pieces, with the game logic and enforcing standard chess rules.
